      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah its like a scavenger hunt but i dont have much time. i'm looking at some options now but everything is just so messy and irrational. like it feels like there's some weird force making everything just go wrong all at once. it's driving me crazy.",
      "source": "evaluator"
